  "body": "Utility::readPacketsFromSocket() use recvmsg to read UDP packets. We can definitely change it to use recvmmsg instead so fewer system calls will be made. And right now it reads till the queue is empty. As we want to limit the number of system calls for each event loop, we can make this function return a bool to indicate the caller if it finishes reading from the socket or not.",
